description: This exclusive collection is a collaboration between 'Fractal Aliens' and 'Fractal Block' features 10 unique BORG Cubes and their paired Drones from the Delta Quadrant and Uncharted Space. Each Cube and Drone is a 'Limited Edition/Unique' NFT, showcasing the advanced technology, adaptive powers, and iconic traits of the Borg Collective. Own a piece of this legendary force, where assimilation is inevitable.
name: Fractal BORG
